</div>]]></content:encoded></item><item><title>【教學】iOS 15.4 公開測試版安裝方法，即用免口罩 Face ID 解鎖</title><link>https://unwire.hk/2022/01/31/ios-15-4-beta/fun-tech/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=ios-15-4-beta</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[Christy]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Mon, 31 Jan 2022 05:46:23 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[科技趣聞]]></category><category><![CDATA[Face ID]]></category><category><![CDATA[iOS 15.4 Beta]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1084039</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>Apple 在 iOS 15.4 加入多個新功能，包括提供戴口罩解鎖 Face ID，為一眾沒有 Apple  [&#8230;]</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>Apple 在 iOS 15.4 加入多個新功能，包括提供戴口罩解鎖 Face ID，為一眾沒有 Apple Watch 的用家帶來喜訊。以下將介紹如何安裝公眾測試版 iOS 15.4。</p><p>早前 Apple 已釋出 iOS 15.4 開發者測試版本，只限開發者下載，如今正式推出公開測試版，只要有 Apple ID 就可下載使用。</p><p>現時戴口罩解鎖 Face ID 功能僅於測試版本 iOS 15.4 Beta 中提供，由於版本現時仍處於測試階段，因此或會出現錯誤，所以建議用家下載前先評估風險，以及事先備份設備數據。另有外媒指出，只有 iPhone 12 或以後的機款才支援戴口罩解鎖 Face ID 功能。</p><p>iOS 15.4 Beta 僅支援以下裝置：</p><p>iPhone 13、iPhone 13 Pro</p><p>iPhone 12、iPhone 12 Mini、iPhone 12 Pro、iPhone 12 Pro Max</p><p>iPhone 11、iPhone 11 Pro、iPhone 11 Pro Max</p><p>iPhone XS、iPhone XS Max</p><p>iPhone X、iPhone XR</p><p>iPhone 8、iPhone 8 Plus</p><p>iPhone 7、iPhone 7 Plus</p><p>iPhone 6S、iPhone 6S Plus</p><p>iPhone SE （第 1、2 代）</p><p>iPod Touch（第 7 代）</p><h2>安裝 iOS 15.4 Beta 教學</h2><h2>Step 1</h2><p>從 Safari 搜尋並進入「Apple Beta Software Program」（Apple Beta 版軟件計劃）。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/IMG_7242.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1084041" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/IMG_7242-346x580.jpg" alt="" width="346" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/IMG_7242-346x580.jpg 346w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/IMG_7242-537x900.jpg 537w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/IMG_7242-768x1287.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/IMG_7242-917x1536.jpg 917w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/IMG_7242.jpg 955w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 346px" /></a></p><h2>Step 2</h2><p>註冊或登入 Apple ID。在網頁上方選擇「Enroll Your Devices」（註冊你的設備）</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/IMG_7243.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1084042" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/IMG_7243-343x580.jpg" alt="" width="343" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/IMG_7243-343x580.jpg 343w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/IMG_7243-532x900.jpg 532w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/IMG_7243-768x1299.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/IMG_7243-908x1536.jpg 908w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/IMG_7243.jpg 946w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 343px" /></a></p><h2>Step 3</h2><p>在「Install profile」（安裝描述文件）中按「Download profile」（下載描述文件）。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/IMG_7244.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1084043" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/IMG_7244-623x580.jpg" alt="" width="623" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/IMG_7244-623x580.jpg 623w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/IMG_7244-966x900.jpg 966w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/IMG_7244-768x715.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/IMG_7244.jpg 1170w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 623px" /></a></p><h2>Step 4</h2><p>選擇「Allow」（允許）後便會彈出提示指「Profile Downloaded」（已下載描述檔）。</p><p>打開「設定」，在上方的「已下載描述檔」選擇「檢視描述檔」。</p><p>點擊右上角「安裝」。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/IMG_7246.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1084045" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/IMG_7246-482x580.jpg" alt="" width="482" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/IMG_7246-482x580.jpg 482w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/IMG_7246-748x900.jpg 748w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/IMG_7246-768x924.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/IMG_7246.jpg 1170w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 482px" /></a></p><h2>Step 5</h2><p>輸入電話鎖機密碼並再次點擊右上角「安裝」。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/IMG_7248.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1084046" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/IMG_7248-294x580.jpg" alt="" width="294" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/IMG_7248-294x580.jpg 294w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/IMG_7248-456x900.jpg 456w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/IMG_7248-768x1517.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/IMG_7248-778x1536.jpg 778w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/IMG_7248-1037x2048.jpg 1037w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/IMG_7248.jpg 810w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 294px" /></a></p><h2>Step 6</h2><p>安裝完成後，重新啟動 iPhone（留意此步驟為必需），進入「一般」＞「軟件更新」便可取得 iOS 15.4 公眾測試版。安裝成後，你便可使用「戴著口罩使用 Face ID」功能。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/IMG_3137.png"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1084156" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/IMG_3137-268x580.png" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/IMG_3137-268x580.png 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/IMG_3137-416x900.png 416w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/IMG_3137-768x1662.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/IMG_3137-710x1536.png 710w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/IMG_3137-947x2048.png 947w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/IMG_3137.png 740w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></a></p><p>資料來源： <a href="https://www.theverge.com/22906798/ios-iphone-15-4-face-id-mask-test-beta">The Verge</a></p><p>—</p><p><u>unwire.hk </u>Mewe 專頁 : <a href="https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk"><u>https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk</u></a></p></p><div class="feedflare">
